            "text": " is a terrible feeling, especially as a car person when you have a deeper connection to your car than most. Now add in a huge helping of sentimental value, and being a victim of car theft can feel awfully personal. That's the scenario one family had to cope with after a modified 1988 ",
            "type": "text",
